    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Source</strong> <em>Inner Sea Intrigue pg. 50</em><br/><strong>Price</strong> 100 gp; <strong>Weight</strong> -<br/><strong>Category</strong> Alchemical Tools</p><h2 class=\"framing\"><img src=\"modules/pf-content/assets/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px;\" title=\"PFS Legal\"/>Description</h2><p>This pill causes the imbiber's skin to shift colors and patterns to match whatever is behind her. As long as a significant portion of her skin is exposed (her head and forearms, for example), the imbiber gains a +4 circumstance bonus on Stealth checks for 4 hours. This bonus doesn't stack with that granted by <em>invisibility</em>, <em>vanish<sup>APG</sup></em>, or similar magical effects. Crafting a chameleon pill requires a successful DC 15 Craft (alchemy) check.</p><h2 class=\"framing\">Construction</h2><p><strong>Craft (Alchemy)</strong> DC 15</p>",
